{"tid":1502990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［極重要］各位手足，試下以「打狗！救人！」取替「推，Push」回覆推Post！","createTime":"2019-08-24T19:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T05:48:56.000Z","uid":33736,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"365928731e62a3103d6b8a607f295b83fa1f9778","tid":1502990,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:02:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>唔明點解要主動出擊嘅同我睇哂呢幾個post</strong><br />\n[屌醒勇武] 不進，則退<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n[圖輯] 香港人呢兩個月既勇武抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502623</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我相信勇武抗爭，就係突破目前局面嘅關鍵<br />\n<br />\n為咗令大家有呢個風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家好似早排「721, 811」、「光復香港，時代革命」咁樣，<br />\n用<strong>「打狗！救人！」</strong>嚟推Po<br />\n<br />\n只要成個連登都係，我相信大家就會慢慢接受到呢個意識，突破到依家嘅心理關口！<br />\n香港人，係時候要以武制暴！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗！救人！<br />\n打狗！救人！<br />\n打狗！救人！<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e457098757903bcab2f473cb13bae4c10a1f0607","tid":1502990,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:03:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗！救人！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7ea2e550acc64b2d05dada729bafe13fa7a9c05b","tid":1502990,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:04:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"41ee7e59ff5b80f7031f728d58d01b6483a82c70","tid":1502990,"uid":160988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"打狗，救